resources.string: Host and manage your code on GitHub.\n You can keep your work private or share it\n with the world.
From hobbyists to professionals, GitHub\n helps developers simplify the way they\n build software.
GitHub is home to millions of open source\n projects. Try one out or get inspired to\n create your own.
One platform, from start to finish
With hundreds of integrations, GitHub is\n flexible enough to be at the center of your\n development process.
